  "body": "2k-stargazers celebration!\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nTo package managers:\r\n* Dev dependency `libpci` should be dropped and `hwdata` should be added as an recommended runtime dependency instead.\r\n* Fastfetch no longer uses `libpci` / `pciutils` in GPU module. However, we still use `hwdata` / `pci.ids` to convert device id to its marketing name.\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n* Support Lxterminal version detection (Terminal, Linux)\r\n* Support weston-terminal version (Terminal, Linux)\r\n* Support `am` package manager detection (#771, Packages, Linux)\r\n* Support network prefix length detection for IPv6 (LocalIP)\r\n* Display all IPs when multiple IPs are assigned to the same interface (LocalIP)\r\n* Add option `--localip-show-prefix-len` to show network prefix length for both IPv4 and IPv6. Defaults to `true` (LocalIP)\r\n\r\nBugfixes:\r\n* Fix network prefix length detection when the value is greater than 24 (#773, LocalIP, Linux)\r\n* For xfce4-terminal, use system mono font if no config file is found (TerminalFont, Linux)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<details><summary>SHA256SUMs</summary><br>\r\n\r\n```\r\na2696f68ffc43f3ff602f360da5bef6d2c922cf1ee1f32b0e87d29e1da838643  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.tar.gz\r\nb62b5df97df8c0e447687841ff8d796ed3d8b502b5808143b526beaca95614c7  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.zip\r\n057083dd91b73851149579538d33f0aa514873b8c2b17fee9aa7acf82ff074b2  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.tar.gz\r\nef26ee798f450cfd4450e0457d299a3f8a25a32e3172b09d788ba08da58336d7  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.zip\r\n2f79782cce4058c9963e45c956a7e466e06d1304bab510831f7cedc725608e0a  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.deb\r\n0476a0f8d97980271c0699d4e6b31eb60a1a192ca3aa87d259a2de35f83401fa  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.rpm\r\n37733b6874c2f70198156ef053ce575d6f4451c96d650141a2b2e1675df75d7f  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n7cdc005ac8a45fcf21612cb